{"tid":1874164,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如何才能確診武漢肺炎？","createTime":"2020-02-11T04:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T06:52:06.000Z","uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e5226eb0ee3fb481e9c8f8bcc67ab1c5a8b95a","tid":1874164,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"如何才能確診武漢肺炎？<br />\n<br />\n1.需要有齊武漢肺炎所有病徵<br />\n2.需要官方認可醫生確認<br />\n3.需要官方認可醫院確認<br />\n4.需要使用官方認可的檢測方法下確診<br />\n5.需在十四天內發病<br />\n6.需要發燒高於38度<br />\n7.需要在官方指定隔離地點十四天內發病<br />\n8.需要確認與確診者有直接接觸"},{"pid":"59c46a3a233e2e7ca6331eb785a5ce8933d3022c","tid":1874164,"uid":131188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"9. 需要官方認可治癒"},{"pid":"47785f01f91920062d196d1b32a529992d3f1e8e","tid":1874164,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:58:11.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家加上個標準"},{"pid":"327b884d95423e3316ecaf30fb9d9537299f17eb","tid":1874164,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"要醫院有位"},{"pid":"d6c6bbecfef8b677a129475975d974860a55a4c0","tid":1874164,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T05:00:13.000Z","msg":"11. 病人發病前需曾到武漢"},{"pid":"453d01bc428e4d431bfe50f4ee6a804544b31a18","tid":1874164,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"PCR<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.prrs.com/en/prrs/diagnostics/visurs-pcr/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prrs.com%2Fen%2Fprrs%2Fdiagnostics%2Fvisurs-pcr%2F&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=12e7c65b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.prrs.com/en/prrs/diagnostics/visurs-pcr/</a>"},{"pid":"39c3d24bf72b37c10ecae84f431dc72638791499","tid":1874164,"uid":126133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"12.需在死亡前確診<br />\n13.需支付5萬蚊檢驗費"},{"pid":"ba5b4e96c7f41c4816530176de9